00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:34.650
Matayog ka at hiwalay.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.960
Mababaw ako sa kaibuturan.

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.360
Gusto ko lang gawin ang best ko

00:10:39.630 --> 00:10:41.360
