Prinsipe Annan,

00:12:42.170 --> 00:12:43.440
anong maitutulong ko sayo?

00:12:49.790 --> 00:12:51.480
Naalala ko sinabi mo

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:53.800
pagkatapos ng pagkatalo sa Lucheng,

00:12:54.270 --> 00:12:56.080
hinanap mo ako kung saan-saan

00:12:56.550 --> 00:12:57.360
at sa wakas

00:12:58.600 --> 00:13:00.360
Natagpuan ako sa Taijin.

00:13:01.190 --> 00:13:01.920
Oo.

00:13:01.940 --> 00:13:02.740
