at tindig

00:13:24.090 --> 00:13:25.950
walang ordinaryong tao ang makakapantay.

00:13:26.270 --> 00:13:27.270
hindi ko nakita

00:13:27.630 --> 00:13:29.030
ang lalaking sinabi mo.

00:13:33.160 --> 00:13:34.070
Prinsipe Annan,

00:13:34.100 --> 00:13:35.910
bakit bigla kang nagtatanong tungkol dito?

00:13:35.910 --> 00:13:37.710
