na subukan ito kahit isang beses nitong mga nakaraang araw,

00:17:30.860 --> 00:17:33.120
alam mo sana na hindi ito bitter.

00:17:38.950 --> 00:17:40.080
Idinagdag mo…

00:17:42.110 --> 00:17:43.440
